          </a>
      </div>
  </section>
  <div id="home">
    <div class="big-bg">
        <%= image_tag "main-bg.jpeg" %>
    </div>
      <div class="home-set">
              <div class="page-title">
                  <h2>毎日の連絡をもっと簡単に</h2>
                  <p>スマホで手軽に連絡しよう!</p>
              </div>
              <div class="inquiry__nav">
                  <p>お問い合わせはこちら➡️</p>
                  <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdu_OQl4cJPiemyEF9rMOyl8b5G06Jp02pK0Xc_ISqVa8s1yQ/viewform?usp=sf_link" width="100%" height="1301" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" class="btn">
